{
  "stem": "12337.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in a barn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The barn had two sides-- on each side of the barn there was a haystack.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the middle, there was a concrete where you could put horses, but there were no horses at the time.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the reason I say that is because later on in my story, it's significant why I mention it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our hole was near the outside wall of the barn, right near the slats of the barn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was very small.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were all sitting, squashed together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father was always in a bending position.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I, as a child, could sit normally, but he had to have his head always bent down because it wasn't that big.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, it was just a very small area for the three of us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If one wanted to turn all three of us had to turn the same time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as far as clothing and washing, we wore the same clothes for 18 months.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We never washed our hands or face once.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Pavlo, the only way he would get near us, he had a dog named [?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Briskov ?] and he would whistle-- that dog saved our lives.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Every time that he wanted to go near us he would whistle for the dog.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the dog would come and he would say something, whisper to the dog, and the dog would go running around, all around the farm, and then come back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And if he told him nobody was around, that's when he would come near us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So that dog was our life saver.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If someone was nearby, that dog would be barking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He wouldn't go near us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So her was safer to go-- he could go near us.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
